"   <div class=\"block pha drugH1Div\" id=\"F7914497\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Mechanism of Action",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Opacification of vessels and anatomical structures in the path of flow of the contrast media which allows for radiographic visualization",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block phk drugH1Div\" id=\"F7914499\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Pharmacodynamics/Kinetics",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;\">",
"     Half-life, elimination: 2 hours; prolonged in renal impairment",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;\">",
"     Excretion: Urine (80% to 90% unchanged)",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
